{"tid":210220,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(2017年4月下旬）低壓槽持續為本港帶來不穩定的天氣","createTime":"2017-04-20T18:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T19:10:07.000Z","uid":38255,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f567923e96d9fd16ac124bc362d847c1cb7ba5f","tid":210220,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:30:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><img src=\"http://x.co/wk017\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk017&h=0677eeb4&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">氣象討論：2017年4月下旬</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此帖文討論期：2017年4月21日至30日</span></strong></span><br />\n【註】 氣象討論帖一般逢每月1日、11日及21日發出新帖文。　當新帖文發出後，或有颱風追擊帖發出，原有的氣象討論帖會隨即停用。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。　以下圖片會自動更新。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><ins>◤溫度術語</ins></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">嚴寒 　　　　　≦ 7 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">寒冷 　 　　　8 - 12 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">清涼　　　　13 - 17 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">和暖／稍涼　18 - 22 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">溫暖　　　　23 - 27 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">炎熱　　　　28 - 32 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">酷熱 　　 　　≧ 33 &deg;C</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>◤參考網頁</ins></span></span><br />\n◆ 認識天氣現象：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Feducation%2Fedu01met_c.htm&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=59205e16\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm</a><br />\n◆ 各類天氣術語：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Fflw_description%2Fflw_c.htm&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=1ae1d3f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm</a><br />\n◆ 各類警告定義：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/explain/introc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Ftextonly%2Fexplain%2Fintroc.htm&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e8d44800\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/explain/introc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 短期氣候預測：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/season/seasonc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fseason%2Fseasonc.htm&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=db2861e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/season/seasonc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 香港天文台電腦預測：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/nhm/nhm_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fnhm%2Fnhm_uc.htm&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=1ac85afc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/nhm/nhm_uc.htm</a><br />\n◆ ECMWF數值預報：<a href=\"http://x.co/ECMWF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FECMWF&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=7e58708b\" target=\"_blank\">http://x.co/ECMWF</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/SuV1UB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FSuV1UB&h=aa5b9639&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/1mOf5kb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F1mOf5kb&h=f43ed746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 地面天氣圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2a5ticH\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2a5ticH&h=b05f53f9&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/2ahInaZ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ahInaZ&h=2a1d8db0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2ajChbn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ajChbn&h=22f823b8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/2ap2lTE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ap2lTE&h=475ff2cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 衛星雲圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2a7TpCM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2a7TpCM&h=ef01e17d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://x.co/1Oc5V\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2F1Oc5V&h=2e7774ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/Meu94L\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FMeu94L&h=e469b653&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/pSSahs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FpSSahs&h=61ae872d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 熱帶系統分佈</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">氣象台專頁正式登場</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>我們自2008年起發表氣象帖。現在，一個屬於巴打絲打們的天氣專頁正式登場！我們以淺白易明的方式介紹氣象，讓您享受認識氣象箇中的樂趣。氣象不再沉悶空泛。<br />\n本專頁旨在為大家提供氣象相關的資訊，其中包括一些氣象小資料、即時的天氣及風暴等消息。設立的主要目的，是為了讓比較忙碌的巴打絲打們，即使沒時間或沒留意到高登氣象帖，都可透過另一個渠道獲得我們的氣象資訊。<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">請巴打絲打們到專頁讚好以示對我們支持及鼓勵</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/FBlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FFBlike&h=5fdd3157&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=51bdd6e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/TWlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FTWlike&h=e9b064ef&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=458f2c7c\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/UTube\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FUTube&h=a22db7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://youtube.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2FHKGweather&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=ea7e2ceb\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/HKGweather</a></em></strong>"},{"pid":"453421c63869f0bafb7d190a52f216dda2868267","tid":210220,"uid":37210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T19:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06d9959d16cb82f92afdbd457078e0733706c3e","tid":210220,"uid":79373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T22:51:40.000Z","msg":"索布斯基留名<br />\n啲雨又miss咗大交合總部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過屯門好大雨"},{"pid":"b33ca78f41df1697bb37d72eb717423b8da1a7f0","tid":210220,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb50c4c80035e11b608d469390f7785ca3bf518c","tid":210220,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:48:31.000Z","msg":"綠茶留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ec735c40ec9f5f14e989423d62ba2a006e99f1","tid":210220,"uid":41177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:13:12.000Z","msg":"Woo hooo"},{"pid":"5499ae180286c94267d50d953a6e73515f460834","tid":210220,"uid":42440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 